# shellcheck shell=bash
use flake
layout node

# No automatic secret loading. Earlier this auto-loaded `.env`/`.env.local`
# (template default) and sourced `.envrc.private` — but ANY secret placed in the
# direnv environment becomes readable by every subprocess run in the repo (package
# scripts, git hooks, formatters, tests, dependency postinstalls), a token-leak
# surface. The repo needs no ambient secrets; set any you need in your own shell.
